      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Motion-Law: Constant-Acceleration and-Deceleration</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Constant-Acceleration and Constant-Deceleration Cam-Law, Motion-Law</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">A </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Cam-Laws" anchor="Standard" styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Traditional Motion-Law</link><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">. &#160;Its name is often reduced to </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Poly345</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion-Values</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">CAN</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> specify the:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Position</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> usually </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">flows</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> from the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Previous-Segment" styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</link><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">.</text></para>
                <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Parameter" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Position</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">CANNOT</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> specify the:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#333399;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Velocity, End-Velocity</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Acceleration, End-Acceleration</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Jerk, End-Jerk</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment Parameters</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">None</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Range</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="2" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#333399;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Range </text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End- Range</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Parameter-Header"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">0 ≤ Start-Range &lt; End-Range ≤ 1</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion-Description (default)</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">It is a Dwell-Rise-Dwell type segment. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The velocity increases from zero to a maximum, then decreases to a zero.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">There is a constant acceleration followed with a constant deceleration. There is an instant cross-over from acceleration to deceleration. It has three </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Acceleration Discontinuities (infinite Jerk)</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">. &#160;It is not recommend for high-speed machinery.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso"><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">See also : </text><image src="MD-Globe-www-24.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:7pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="weblink" href="http://mechdesigner.support/index.htm?mt-tutorial-5-edit-start-standard-segment.htm" target="_blank" styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Tutorial 5: Edit the Start of a Traditional Motion-Law</link><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso"><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">See also : </text><image src="MD-Globe-www-24.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:7pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="weblink" href="http://mechdesigner.support/index.htm?tutorial-9-asymmetrical-motions.htm" target="_blank" styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Tutorial 9: Asymmetrical Motions.</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
